data.description: Welcome to this beautifully remodeled 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with a large back yard great for entertaining. Conveniently located near I-20 and I-35, this house has been transformed from top to bottom in 2022. The exterior boasts new brick, siding, a back porch, roof, windows, landscaping, and driveway. Inside, you'll find all-new flooring, a modern kitchen, upgraded restrooms, AC, electrical systems, plumbing, and a tankless water heater, along with fresh paint throughout. The living room and dining room boast an excellent open concept, flooded with abundant natural light.  The master bedroom features a spacious walk-in closet and his-and-hers vanities in the bathroom, complete with a stunning stand-up shower. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this turnkey home!
